<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
    <title>Multi-Step Authentication Verification</title>
    <style>
      body {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f9fafb;
        color: #111827;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 1080px;
        margin: 40px auto;
        background: white;
        border-radius: 12px;
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: 0 10px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
      }
      .header {
        background-color: #0f172a;
        color: #ffffff;
        padding: 24px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 30px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .content h2 {
        margin-top: 0;
        font-size: 22px;
        font-weight: 600;
      }
      .step {
        background-color: #f3f4f6;
        padding: 18px;
        margin: 15px 0;
        border-left: 6px solid #2563eb;
        text-align: left;
        border-radius: 6px;
      }
      .step strong {
        color: #1f2937;
      }
      .otp-box {
        font-size: 26px;
        letter-spacing: 4px;
        font-weight: bold;
        background-color: #0f172a;
        color: whitesmoke;
        padding: 14px 28px;
        border-radius: 10px;
        display: inline-block;
        margin: 20px 0;
        text-transform: uppercase;
      }
      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        margin-top: 20px;
        padding: 12px 24px;
        background-color: #2563eb;
        color: white !important;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 6px;
        font-weight: 500;
      }
      .footer {
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #6b7280;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 20px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>{{health}}</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <h2>Multi-Step Authentication Verification</h2>
        <p>Hello {{to}},</p>
        <p>
          To complete the authentication process, please follow the steps below and verify your identity:
        </p>

        <div class="step">
          <strong>Step 1:</strong> Enter the following OTP code:
           <div style="text-align: center;">
    <div class="otp-box">{{otp}}</div>
  </div>
        </div>

        <div class="step">
          <strong>Step 2:</strong> Click the verification button below to proceed to the second authentication step.
        </div>

        <a class="button" href="{{link}}">Continue Verification</a>

        <p style="margin-top: 20px;">
          This verification code and link will expire in 5 minutes for your security.
        </p>

        <p>If you didnâ€™t attempt to sign in or enable authentication, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        &copy; {{year}} {{health}}. All rights reserved.
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
